snippet.title: [APRIL FOOLS 2023] POOSTALL Royale Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
We can't believe we're not charging you for this majestic masterpiece! 
Don't let the title fool you, this isn't a battle royale game.

Maybe this isn't even a game at all... well, just download now and figure it out!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2362740/POOSTALL_Royale/
